This plugin embeds your connatix ad for you. Simple managing with graphic interface.

== Description ==

This plugin embeds your connatix ad for you. Simple managing with graphic interface.




== Installation ==

1. Download and unzip the zip file. Copy the folder `connatix` with all of its contents to the `/wp-content/plugins/` directory
2. Activate the plugin through the `Plugins` menu in WordPress Admin Interface.
3. Go to 'Settings' menu in the Admin Interface (Connatix Plugin) and and use the GUI to set up your ad.
4. Click 'Save Changes' and you're done. That's all!


